track_notes: Mt Grammondo is tiring walk, you will disurb the 2 points!!! this starting point must be reach only if you have a 4x4 car. the landscape is very nice; in summer time get lot of water and dont forget hat or cap. Plenty room on summit for antenna, but summit is very crowded!
